snippet: A former Iowa lawmaker has pleaded guilty to federal charges stemming from his switch of support from one Republican candidate for president to another before the 2012 caucuses, federal prosecutors said Wednesday....

headline.print_headline: Ex-Lawmaker Pleads Guilty in GOP Caucuses Case
headline.main: Ex-Lawmaker Pleads Guilty in GOP Caucuses Case

lead_paragraph: A former Iowa lawmaker has pleaded guilty to federal charges stemming from his switch of support from one Republican candidate for president to another before the 2012 caucuses, federal prosecutors said Wednesday.
